  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the planned book by George R.R. Martin, see <a href=\"/index.php/Blood_%26_Fire\" title=\"Blood &amp; Fire\">Blood &amp; Fire</a>.</div>\n<p><i><b>Blood and Fire</b></i> is a fragmentary, anonymous, blood-soaked tome containing information about <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragons</a>.  It is sometimes called <i><b>The Death of Dragons</b></i>. The only surviving copy is supposedly hidden away in a locked vault beneath the <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Blood_and_Fire&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_14\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 14\">Chapter 14</a>, Tyrion IV.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403141018\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.031 seconds\nRea